summary: Marvel Leaks Plot Details of Avengers: Endgame Ending
title: Marvel Leaks Plot Details of Avengers: Endgame Ending
body:
Marvel Leaks Plot Details of Avengers: Endgame Ending

This year, Marvel gave us its best movie yet in Avengers: Infinity War, with an ending that not only left us all in shock thanks to the decimation, but set up a lot of juicy things to look forward to in Avengers: Endgame… and now Marvel has raised our anticipation even further with details of what to expect.

The news comes from a Marvel press release leaked on Imgur, that is translated below.…

title: Running From My Shadow
body:
Loki has escaped the Asgard prison, again.

Soft Praise To a Hard Lie

It had become one of his favorite hobbies, if not the only one. Sneaking out of prison every other day was something that filled Loki with joy, whether it was to steal something or play pranks on Thor…
